room_title: Escape room "The Explorers' Club" by Escape2Win in Virginia Beach
room_description: –ùou are one of the lucky few who have been invited to the world-renowned explorers' club! You have an hour to locate a priceless artifact hidden decades ago by the founder of the club himself. It lies hidden among a collection of curiosities, oddities and relics from all over the globe. Be careful: if you fail to find the artifact in one hour, you may join his collection forever!
